    "body": "@ondras Thanks for the investigation work, after looking into wmctrl and Chromium's source code, the only difference seems to be wmctrl calling `XMapRaised` after sending the `_NET_ACTIVE_WINDOW` message, we should probably do the same in Electron.\n"
